{"tid":1743134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選舉前幾日 重啟食窮建制派策略","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T11:38:43.000Z","uid":20473,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"90e69edde6f8c934f1c44a6271564dc51b1d3e74","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:35:03.000Z","msg":"同十幾年前食窮民建聯其實一樣<br />\n都係同啲貪小便宜既師奶阿叔講<br />\n投建制派使佢地當選 佢哋會得到較少著數<br />\n<br />\n如果窮撚民主派贏左 有政府錢派著數<br />\n建制派因為輸左又會加budget 派蛇齋餅糭<br />\n所以你有兩份禮物收<br />\n<br />\n而建制贏左 佢哋都係派返呢份蛇齋餅糭俾你<br />\n窮撚因爲冇經費 就派唔到野<br />\n你只有一份禮物收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識諗都知要選邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f6da93c7c368d447ea60dbcd17b3f8e610f234","tid":1743134,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"今個星期主線︰<br />\n團結絕殺保皇黨 ! <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1737525/</a>"},{"pid":"14c3e0a2b445cdc37d97318962389e83f5b14562","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c8637173e2fcf0cf57e05e0ad7245563dbaf7369","tid":1743134,"uid":252292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"919065b922c8f257e3fffd4cc94f991463cd37f9","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c3e0a2b445cdc37d97318962389e83f5b14562","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"b856e7c9cc4664d2911c263739eed0e0705dd003","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"919065b922c8f257e3fffd4cc94f991463cd37f9","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c3e0a2b445cdc37d97318962389e83f5b14562","tid":1743134,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":